description: This ask a series of questions about identifying features of the vehicle to assist in determining the model year of the vehicle.  The user will just need to start the skill with a start phrase such as "Alexa, start unofficial Willys year"
imageAltText: Unofficial Willys wagon and truck year identifier icon
name: Unofficial Willys wagon and truck year identifier
shortDescription: This will assist in determining the model year of a Willys wagon or pickup truck vehicle
